<ul>
    <li>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><font face="Times New Roman, serif"><font face="Times New Roman, serif"><font size="3">RAA: 	Real time Asset Allocation analysis for mutual funds and ETFs. This 	allows users to track down the asset exposure in a mutual fund 	(usually a flexible allocation fund, a balance or conservative 	fund). For example, GMO Alpha Only III (GGHEX) is an institutional 	fund which requires minimum 10 million US dollars to invest. 	However, using this tool, one could monitor and mimic its allocation 	in real time. </font></font><font face="Times New Roman, serif"><font size="3"><i><b>See 	demo here.</b></i></font></font></font></p>
    </li>
